Name: MegaMart
Description: A large supermarket offering an extensive selection of products, including fresh produce, dairy, household items, and popular snacks like chips. Known for its competitive pricing, variety, and wide range of everyday essentials, making it a convenient one-stop shop for all your grocery needs.

Name: MehdiMark
Description: Extensive selection of international and local food items. Daily fresh stock of fruits, vegetables, and pantry essentials.

Name: BigValue Superstore
Description: Temporarily closed for renovations. Offers a variety of bulk items and discounted goods."

Name: FreshMart
Description: A neighborhood grocery store focused on fresh, organic produce and artisanal dairy products. Offers a curated selection of locally-sourced goods.

Name: Frahmand
Description: Known for its farm-to-table approach, FreshMart is committed to high-quality fresh vegetables and fruits with an emphasis on sustainability.

Name: Local Delights Grocery
Description: Closed for inventory restocking. Usually offers fresh, locally-sourced vegetables and fruits.

Name: Dave's Butcher Shop
Description: Specializes in fresh cuts of meat, including locally-sourced poultry, beef, and pork. Offers custom cuts and ready-to-cook marinated options.

Name: Prime Cuts Butcher
Description: Temporarily closed due to supplier issues. Known for rare cuts and exotic meats.

Name: Alice's Bakery
Description: A family-owned bakery offering a wide variety of freshly baked bread, pastries, and cakes. Known for its all-natural ingredients and traditional recipes.

Name: Ston's Bakery

Name: Bread & Butter Bakery
Description: Renowned for its handcrafted sourdough and artisan bread. Offers a selection of freshly made croissants and cookies.

Name: Reza Pharmacy
Description: A highly-rated pharmacy known for its exceptional customer service and wide range of medications. Specializes in both prescription and over-the-counter products, catering to diverse healthcare needs in the community.

Description: A specialized cardiology clinic providing advanced treatment for heart conditions. Equipped with the latest diagnostic technology and personalized care plans.

Description: A specialized cardiology clinic providing advanced treatment for heart conditions. Equipped with the latest diagnostic technology and personalized care plans.

Name: Almas Hotel
Description: A luxurious hotel offering premium accommodations and exceptional service in Shiraz. Features elegant rooms a fine dining restaurant a spa and conference facilities making it ideal for both leisure and business travelers.
